definitions.definition: An unsaturated hydrocarbon , C 5 H 8 , that is readily polymerized ; natural rubber ( caoutchouc ) is cis-1,4-polyisoprene, and trans-1,4-polyisoprene is present in gutta-percha and balata ; it is the structural basis for the terpenes .

main_definition: ( organic chemistry ) An unsaturated hydrocarbon , C 5 H 8 , that is readily polymerized ; natural rubber ( caoutchouc ) is cis-1,4-polyisoprene, and trans-1,4-polyisoprene is present in gutta-percha and balata ; it is the structural basis for the terpenes .
